overview:
Designit is a global strategic design and innovation firm.

With 290+ professionals working out of 14 offices in 11 countries, we help ambitious companies make innovation happen. Our aim is to create strong and sustainable business value through strategy and design.

Working across the entire customer experience, the company creates products, services and experiences that drive customer engagement and help realize business growth.
